.playwright-mcp/

# Working screenshots from development — intermediate and rejected iterations.
# Only the two the README shows are tracked.
screenshots/*
!screenshots/v11-release-front.png
!screenshots/live-phone-final.png

# The worker's dependencies, not the worker.
worker/node_modules/
worker/.wrangler/

# The Cloudflare API token lives here and NOWHERE else — never in git, never in
# chat, never in a screenshot. A committed token is a worker someone else owns.
worker/.env
.env

# vendor/ is deliberately NOT ignored: three.module.min.js is the whole point of
# vendoring it. Ignore it and the deployed site loses its watch.
